WEBVTT

00:01:51.159 --> 00:01:52.640
Zhao Qishan

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:55.359
You finally got what you deserved.

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:40.159
The Police Department will continue

00:02:40.159 --> 00:02:42.520
to fully combat all criminal activities

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:43.879
and restore to the citizens of Tai Cheng

00:02:43.879 --> 00:02:46.520
a safe and secure social environment.

00:02:52.319 --> 00:02:53.479
What happened?

00:02:54.120 --> 00:02:55.719
Why is this happening again now?

00:03:06.039 --> 00:03:06.960
Inspector Qi, over here.

00:03:09.719 --> 00:03:10.520
What's the situation?

00:03:10.719 --> 00:03:12.039
Officer He is leading the investigation.

00:03:12.280 --> 00:03:14.080
Two victims in the top-floor study, a man and a woman.

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:15.680
The woman was burned beyond recognition.

00:03:16.120 --> 00:03:17.759
Preliminary findings indicate accelerants were used.

00:03:18.520 --> 00:03:19.719
Have the victims been identified?

00:03:20.520 --> 00:03:21.719
Yes, it's the owners of the house.

00:03:21.719 --> 00:03:22.520
The woman is Di Fu.

00:03:22.520 --> 00:03:23.319
She's an internet celebrity.

00:03:23.680 --> 00:03:24.599
The man is Zhao Qishan.

00:03:24.599 --> 00:03:25.280
He was stabbed multiple times.

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:26.199
Babel Tower.

00:03:26.479 --> 00:03:27.719
Let's go up and take a look.

00:03:42.439 --> 00:03:43.639
Have you checked the surveillance here?

00:03:44.520 --> 00:03:45.360
The cameras were all turned off.

00:03:45.879 --> 00:03:46.400
Wait a minute.

00:03:56.520 --> 00:03:57.919
Get me the autopsy report the moment it's ready.

00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:04.800
Chief He.

00:04:05.479 --> 00:04:06.159
I heard them say

00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:07.319
your deduction is that

00:04:07.319 --> 00:04:09.159
Zhao Qishan's wife, Di Fu, killed him

00:04:09.879 --> 00:04:10.759
and then set herself on fire to escape punishment.

00:04:11.479 --> 00:04:14.479
Twenty-five stabs to the chest and abdomen. Brutal.

00:04:17.720 --> 00:04:18.279
Qi Yuan.

00:04:18.600 --> 00:04:19.800
You're about to be transferred.

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:22.319
Leave the case to someone else.

00:04:22.639 --> 00:04:23.839
Have the victims' families been notified?

00:04:24.279 --> 00:04:26.399
Zhao Qishan has a younger brother named Zhao Qihai.

00:04:26.560 --> 00:04:27.600
He has been notified.

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:28.879
His wife, Di Fu,

00:04:29.759 --> 00:04:31.319
whose real name was Li Ren,

00:04:31.879 --> 00:04:34.360
has a younger sister who hasn't been found yet.

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:35.399
A sister?

00:04:36.040 --> 00:04:36.839
Ms. Li Ran.

00:04:37.279 --> 00:04:39.360
As your sister and brother-in-law's Retained Counsel,

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:42.399
I will help them fulfill their final wishes today.

00:04:42.879 --> 00:04:44.399
This is Ms. Di Fu,

00:04:44.519 --> 00:04:46.279
your sister Li Ren,

00:04:46.399 --> 00:04:47.879
and your brother-in-law Zhao Qishan's will.

00:04:48.079 --> 00:04:48.639
Please take a look.

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:50.519
How did my sister die?

00:04:51.639 --> 00:04:53.120
According to the current police report,

00:04:54.319 --> 00:04:56.920
Ms. Li Ren killed Mr. Zhao Qishan,

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:58.120
then committed suicide by fire to escape punishment.

00:04:58.279 --> 00:04:59.319
It was a suicide pact.

00:05:00.040 --> 00:05:02.399
Ms. Li Ren and Mr. Zhao Qishan have passed away.

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:03.279
The reasons behind it

00:05:03.279 --> 00:05:05.120
no longer matter.

00:05:05.560 --> 00:05:06.519
What matters is you,

00:05:06.879 --> 00:05:07.680
Ms. Li Ran.

00:05:08.600 --> 00:05:10.720
You are the heir to their assets worth hundreds of millions.

00:05:14.879 --> 00:05:16.120
Is the case just closed like this?

00:05:17.360 --> 00:05:18.439
The condition of the scene,

00:05:18.439 --> 00:05:19.439
the suicide notes from both,

00:05:19.439 --> 00:05:20.680
and the lawyer's testimony all prove

00:05:20.680 --> 00:05:22.199
that this case is just that simple.

00:05:22.519 --> 00:05:24.800
Twenty-five stabs for a suicide pact? Do you believe that?

00:05:26.199 --> 00:05:27.920
It is clearly written in the suicide note.

00:05:28.040 --> 00:05:29.680
The wife, Di Fu, suffered from leukemia.

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:31.199
The husband would rather die with her.

00:05:31.199 --> 00:05:32.360
He asked his wife to kill him,

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:33.199
and then she committed suicide.

00:05:33.480 --> 00:05:34.279
Give me an explanation.

00:05:34.439 --> 00:05:35.160
Why?

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:37.600
Why do you have so many questions?

00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:38.720
They were just a pair of hopeless romantics.

00:05:39.319 --> 00:05:40.720
The case is closed, understand?

00:05:41.959 --> 00:05:43.000
Di Fu's sister,

00:05:43.160 --> 00:05:43.759
Li Ran.

00:05:45.399 --> 00:05:47.000
Old Qi, I'll tell you one more time.

00:05:47.680 --> 00:05:48.279
The case is closed.

00:06:22.759 --> 00:06:24.079
The police have announced it's closed.

00:06:24.279 --> 00:06:25.360
They have already withdrawn from the villa.

00:06:25.959 --> 00:06:27.000
Tomorrow morning at ten o'clock,

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:28.879
please arrive at the Babel Tower villa on time.

00:06:29.240 --> 00:06:31.519
At that time, I will announce your status as heir

00:06:31.519 --> 00:06:32.839
and the allocation of the inheritance.

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:39.199
Auntie Ma, did you drug us?

00:06:39.399 --> 00:06:40.839
You crazy woman, what are you doing?

00:06:41.319 --> 00:06:42.160
Don't be afraid.

00:06:42.920 --> 00:06:45.160
I just wanted you all to calm down.

00:06:45.759 --> 00:06:46.879
This is getting more and more interesting.

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:02.480
Hello, I am...

00:07:02.480 --> 00:07:03.480
You must be Ms. Li Ran.

00:07:04.879 --> 00:07:07.079
I am A Si, the villa's butler.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:08.879
Welcome. Please come in.

00:07:12.120 --> 00:07:13.240
Has Lawyer Luo arrived?

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:15.279
Not yet. Please come in.

00:07:40.519 --> 00:07:41.360
Distinguished guests,

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:43.560
this is Ms. Li Ran,

00:07:44.199 --> 00:07:45.079
the Madam's younger sister.

00:07:46.480 --> 00:07:47.040
Now that someone

00:07:48.759 --> 00:07:50.519
from Di Fu's family has arrived...

00:07:50.519 --> 00:07:51.920
You've got some nerve.

00:07:52.399 --> 00:07:54.519
That crazy woman killed my brother.

00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:56.680
Don't think that burning herself to death

00:07:56.680 --> 00:07:58.079
puts an end to everything.

00:07:58.439 --> 00:07:59.160
Ah Hai.

00:08:00.199 --> 00:08:01.800
The police said it was a suicide pact.

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:04.720
We must trust the police.

00:08:05.199 --> 00:08:07.120
Ms. Li, I'm Fang Qiu.

00:08:07.319 --> 00:08:08.920
I'm a friend of Mr. Zhao.

00:08:09.199 --> 00:08:11.399
I was also acquainted with your sister.

00:08:11.920 --> 00:08:14.959
Acquainted? You mean very close.

00:08:15.800 --> 00:08:18.759
I'm afraid Di Fu knew exactly

00:08:19.319 --> 00:08:22.199
how many hairs were on Mr. Fang's body.

00:08:25.279 --> 00:08:26.680
Let me do the introductions.

00:08:27.519 --> 00:08:28.920
This is Mr. Fang Qiu,

00:08:29.319 --> 00:08:31.279
a good friend of the Master and Madam.

00:08:32.240 --> 00:08:33.720
This is Mr. Tan Tian,

00:08:34.159 --> 00:08:35.799
the Master's business partner.

00:08:36.919 --> 00:08:38.720
This is Mr. Zhao Qihai,

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:40.120
the Master's younger brother.

00:08:41.320 --> 00:08:42.679
That is Auntie Ma Shan.

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:44.279
There are ghosts!

00:08:44.879 --> 00:08:46.360
There are ghosts in this house!

00:08:47.159 --> 00:08:49.320
This crazy hag is at it again.

00:08:49.320 --> 00:08:50.919
When will Lawyer Luo arrive?

00:08:52.759 --> 00:08:56.720
Ghosts killed Zhao Qishan and Di Fu!

00:09:01.639 --> 00:09:02.360
Ms. Li,

00:09:03.440 --> 00:09:04.159
don't pay any attention to her.

00:09:04.679 --> 00:09:06.919
She's lost her mind.

00:09:09.759 --> 00:09:11.080
Lawyer Luo instructed that

00:09:11.759 --> 00:09:14.200
everyone mentioned in the will must be present,

00:09:14.759 --> 00:09:17.600
so we have all gathered here.

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:34.879
A Si, are there really ghosts here?

00:09:35.279 --> 00:09:37.120
The previous owner of this house...

00:09:37.480 --> 00:09:39.559
his entire family died here.

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:42.720
As for whether there are actually ghosts,

00:09:43.200 --> 00:09:44.320
I wouldn't know.

00:09:48.039 --> 00:09:48.879
Regarding this place,

00:09:49.320 --> 00:09:51.159
I have actually heard a story.

00:09:52.399 --> 00:09:55.320
It starts with a security guard.

00:10:15.720 --> 00:10:18.000
You must have worked in a haunted house, kid.

00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:24.879
Miss Li, these are all rumors.

00:10:25.080 --> 00:10:26.080
Don't pay too much attention to them.

00:10:26.399 --> 00:10:28.600
It's only real if you believe it.

00:10:29.159 --> 00:10:31.480
Besides, you don't need to worry.

00:10:32.519 --> 00:10:33.879
I will protect you.

00:10:34.759 --> 00:10:35.600
If you ask me,

00:10:35.840 --> 00:10:36.919
there's no smoke without fire.

00:10:37.919 --> 00:10:39.799
Don't you think there's something wrong with this house?

00:10:41.279 --> 00:10:43.320
It feels uncomfortable as soon as you walk in.

00:10:43.679 --> 00:10:44.200
No, no, no.

00:10:44.200 --> 00:10:44.919
Not at all.

00:10:45.120 --> 00:10:46.480
I... I don't get that feeling.

00:10:46.879 --> 00:10:48.279
My brother is dead.

00:10:48.519 --> 00:10:49.879
This house is mine.

00:10:51.440 --> 00:10:51.960
Ghost!

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:56.919
Ghost! A ghost!

00:10:57.559 --> 00:11:00.320
It's not a ghost. It's rocks falling from the mountain.

00:11:01.159 --> 00:11:03.320
Can't be helped with the continuous rain, right?

00:11:05.840 --> 00:11:08.080
A Si, to get out of here,

00:11:08.559 --> 00:11:09.519
there is only one road.

00:11:09.919 --> 00:11:10.360
Yes.

00:11:10.559 --> 00:11:11.799
The road has been completely blocked.

00:11:12.159 --> 00:11:13.120
We can't get out.

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:16.360
Hello, everyone.

00:11:17.200 --> 00:11:18.360
Let me introduce myself.

00:11:18.679 --> 00:11:20.120
My name is Qi Yuan.

00:11:20.960 --> 00:11:22.120
I'm from the Tai Cheng Police Department.

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:25.320
May I ask what you are doing here?

00:11:34.559 --> 00:11:37.279
Inspector Qi, the case is closed.

00:11:38.120 --> 00:11:39.799
We don't need police here, do we?

00:11:40.279 --> 00:11:42.200
I just came to ask,

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:43.799
here,

00:11:45.000 --> 00:11:46.000
who is the owner?

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:47.919
The house belonged to my brother.

00:11:48.200 --> 00:11:50.960
So naturally, the owner is me now.

00:11:53.480 --> 00:11:54.279
Mr. Zhao.

00:11:55.559 --> 00:11:57.159
The will hasn't been announced yet.

00:11:58.279 --> 00:11:59.960
It's not certain whose house this is yet.

00:12:00.919 --> 00:12:01.559
Besides,

00:12:02.120 --> 00:12:04.559
Madam Di Fu's sister, Miss Li, is still here.

00:12:05.720 --> 00:12:07.600
She has a share too, right?

00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:08.120
Her?

00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:11.399
Does she deserve it?

00:12:16.039 --> 00:12:17.519
I'm not here to fight for the inheritance.

00:12:18.600 --> 00:12:20.519
But if there is a share that belongs to me,

00:12:22.200 --> 00:12:23.720
I won't just give it up to you for nothing.

00:12:29.480 --> 00:12:30.919
Why are we arguing?

00:12:32.120 --> 00:12:32.799
Calm down.

00:12:33.679 --> 00:12:34.799
There's a flash flood.

00:12:34.799 --> 00:12:35.919
None of us can leave.

00:12:36.360 --> 00:12:37.480
I just came to ask

00:12:38.039 --> 00:12:39.320
who the owner is here.

00:12:39.879 --> 00:12:40.720
Could you let me

00:12:41.960 --> 00:12:42.559
stay for the night?

00:12:47.240 --> 00:12:48.759
A Si is the housekeeper here.

00:12:49.639 --> 00:12:50.799
Before the will is announced,

00:12:52.120 --> 00:12:53.519
she should be the one in charge here.

00:12:55.519 --> 00:12:56.559
So, can I?

00:12:56.679 --> 00:12:59.120
Of course. The villa has many rooms.

00:12:59.639 --> 00:13:00.080
Thank you.

00:13:12.279 --> 00:13:14.279
This is the Master and Madam's room.

00:13:15.120 --> 00:13:16.519
Do you mind?

00:13:17.159 --> 00:13:17.960
No problem.

00:13:18.159 --> 00:13:19.519
Then please take a rest.

00:13:19.840 --> 00:13:21.519
Lawyer Luo might arrive a bit later.

00:13:22.080 --> 00:13:23.759
We'll just have to wait patiently.

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:25.120
Thank you, A Si.

00:13:59.600 --> 00:14:01.600
You finally said it.

00:14:02.279 --> 00:14:03.639
What is your relationship with Niannian?

00:14:03.960 --> 00:14:05.039
Friends, friends.

00:14:05.039 --> 00:14:06.639
Good friends, Auntie. Good friends.

00:14:06.840 --> 00:14:07.919
Since you are friends,

00:14:08.720 --> 00:14:11.200
why didn't I hear about her in your story?